the first few breaths for you

00:01:05.019 --> 00:01:07.150 align:middle line:84%
to take a moment to
acknowledge that,

00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:11.120 align:middle line:84%
is an act of self-care, a
gift to self-care to yourself.

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:12.167 align:middle line:90%
It could be in the body.

00:01:12.167 --> 00:01:14.500 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to have a shower
whether I'm down in the dumps

00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:14.740 align:middle line:90%
